# LVM Operator Repositories Configuration
# =======================================
#
# Format: repo_url | directory | branch
#
# - Lines starting with # are comments
# - Empty lines are ignored
# - branch: use 'main', 'master', a tag, or a specific branch
#
# All repos are cloned using --filter=blob:none (blobless clone):
# - Full repo structure visible, all files accessible
# - Blob contents fetched on-demand when read
# - Much faster initial clone, smaller disk footprint
# - Perfect for code exploration (not active development)

# Core LVM Operator repositories
https://github.com/openshift/lvm-operator.git | lvm-operator | main
https://github.com/openshift/topolvm.git | topolvm | main

# Prow Tests repo
https://github.com/openshift/release.git | release | master

# Gitlab based repositories used for product management (requires VPN)
https://gitlab.cee.redhat.com/releng/konflux-release-data | konflux-release-data | main
https://gitlab.cee.redhat.com/prodsec/product-definitions | product-definitions | master
